Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) first, then [docs/AGENT_HARNESS.md](docs/AGENT_HARNESS.md) for procedures.

**3-command UI workflow**

1. Once after clone: `./scripts/install-agent-hooks.sh`
2. While iterating UI/auth/routing: `./scripts/dev-watch.sh`
3. Before handoff: `./scripts/ui-change-gate.sh` (or `--tier smoke` for a faster gate)

Do not finish UI work with `cargo build --features ssr` or `cargo run --features ssr`. Git pre-commit and pre-push run `ui-staleness-check.sh`.

**Multi-agent:** five roles + Coordinator — see [docs/MULTI_AGENT_COORDINATION.md](docs/MULTI_AGENT_COORDINATION.md). **MCP:** observe via Vercel/Railway; deploy via scripts — see [docs/MCP_AGENT_WORKFLOW.md](docs/MCP_AGENT_WORKFLOW.md).